{"tid":2171731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有線財務總裁：即時解僱3名工程人員目的是強化新聞部","createTime":"2020-08-24T07:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T08:29:24.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4606c8544cb277c109beec3f1552dd1ea9fca1b7","tid":2171731,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:02:35.000Z","msg":"有線寬頻集團財務總裁郭子健，今早與有線新聞部各主管和員工會晤，解釋日前即時解僱3名工程人員的決定。郭子健說，有關決定是調整公司架構及人力資源的檢討，目的是強化新聞部，以應付未來競爭，強調管理層對各部門包括新聞部的人事架構，擁有管理決策權。<br />\n<br />\n有線寬頻在會面後發出的新聞稿，形容雙方坦誠溝通交流，郭子健向員工說明相關政策及措施，並表示已安排適當人選接任，絕不會影響新聞部日常運作。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545533-20200824.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545533-20200824.htm&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=390efa33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545533-20200824.htm&h=1b431fc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545533-20200824.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c207f0dcf0a02edda3e7ed4c5d7461f141ffbddd","tid":2171731,"uid":228894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:07:50.000Z","msg":"換入支那工程人員...<br />\n所有新聞資料直接送中..."},{"pid":"e077a5f560f2e9ae7658282e7dcc42926b3fb3d4","tid":2171731,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:27:16.000Z","msg":"唔洗解釋咁多，唔想我地抵制就唔好變紅"},{"pid":"94c394690dc26c87f8cbca281d00a795e901045a","tid":2171731,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:29:24.000Z","msg":"強化新聞部染紅速度<br />\n將新聞部中央集權於紅色力量 (新請幾個新聞總監)"}]}